Array<T> - Interface in com.facebook.collections
The idea here is to provide a uniform interface for arrays so that we may implement data structures on top of them seeming to use "Objects", with auto[un]boxing, but the backing storage may be primitive arrays in order to save memory (ex: hash tables implemented in terms of arrays) While this interface doesn't 100% enforce that implementations will be a class array, the implementation should have array-like properties in terms of memory usage and time of operations: get/setshould be O(1).
